                                 License
                                 =======

The FateCall Package is Freeware. You may use it freely as long as the
Program Files (FateCall, FateCallChat) and the Documentation Files
(FateCall.guide) remain unaltered.

                               Distribution
                               ============

The FateCall Package must include the following Files:

FateCall                                FateCallChat
FateCall.cfg                            FateCall.pic
Marky.ansi                              Maz!.ansi
Nebraska.ansi                           FILE_ID.DIZ

